videos.description: Kawhi Leonard follows the miss with the one-handed jam. Not to be outdone by Kristaps Porzingis who goes baseline for the slam.

videos.description: The Mavericks get out in transition, leading to a Kristaps Porzingis dunk to force a Clippers timeout.

videos.description: Tim Hardaway Sr. is fired up after watching his son, Tim Hardaway Jr. put in a layup and a 3.
